title: Ep33: She Get It From Her Mama feat Mandii's Mom
itunes:title: Ep33: She Get It From Her Mama feat Mandii's Mom
description:
You all enjoyed Weezy's mom so much, it only made sense to bring Mandii's mama to the studio. This time in the studio, the duo discuss interracial dating from the perspective of Mandii's white mom and her decisions on dating black men. The kink of the week is accompanied by a crazy story. Also listen to my mom's "Whoreible Decision" that she technically couldn't control. If you haven't yet, be sure to get your tickets to the live show while they are available at whoreibledecisions.eventbrite.com The live show is brought to you by CastSoundLab.
